Sannomiya residence basement. Mastaroon's former
research facility.

Ayano had undergone secret brainwashing and
modification by her grandfather, Ichijo
Dousaburou, also known as Mastaroon.

After undergoing the initial stages of gentle
brainwashing through subtle medication and the use
of sleep brainwashing devices while in an
unconscious state,

Ayano was undergoing full brainwashing through the
use of brainwashing fluid.
